Show links to curation spreadsheets

Source: R/physiologies.R
curationLinks.Rd

Show links to curation spreadsheets

curationLinks(keyword = "all")

Arguments

keyword

a character vector of physiologies desired. For the available physiologies, run bugphyzz::showPhys(). Use "all" for all available physiologies.

Value

a data.frame with physiology names and URLs

Examples
